data.description: Experience the warmth of home in this recently renovated 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence nestled on a 1.11-acre property in Lake Wales.  Conveniently situated near US Hwy 27, one of Florida's primary routes, this home boasts a fully fenced lot adorned with palm and oak trees.  The expansive space allows for ample parking, whether for trucks, pets, boats, RVs, and more – and all without the restrictions of an HOA.  Enhancing privacy is a gated entrance that leads to a welcoming front porch, complemented by a freshly painted exterior and window shutters.  A 2-car covered carport/boathouse and a 20 x 13 storage shed provide additional practicality. Backyard has irrigation for gardening and growing you own fresh veggies.  Inside, discover a fully refurbished interior featuring new wood-look vinyl flooring.  The spacious living room is fitted with a newly installed ceiling fan and light fixtures.  The kitchen is a chef's dream, offering custom shelving, a cooking island with a range, a stainless-steel dishwasher, closet pantry, tiled backsplash, and ample countertop space.  Adjacent to the kitchen is a tastefully appointed dining area with a new light fixture.  Each of the two bedrooms enjoys its own fully refurbished bathroom, complete with new vanities, light and plumbing fixtures, mirrors, toilets, and tiled shower.  Step out the backdoor to savor peaceful views of the yard from the wooden deck. The property also features a utility room on the back porch.  If you seek tranquility, a spacious plot, and an affordably priced, newly refurbished home, your search ends here.  Schedule your appointment today, as this home is ready for viewing.
